Package: fastAnnotator
Title: Fast Annotation Tool for Linguistic Databases
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Timo", "Schuer", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "timo@example.com")
Description: A Shiny-based annotation tool for linguistic databases. Provides
    audio playback, Praat integration, and transcript display for efficient
    annotation of speech data stored in MariaDB databases.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
